object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (		
    SELECT 		
        bls.batch_id,		
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,		
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime		
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls		
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'		
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'		
      AND bls.batch_id = (		
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)		
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary		
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'		
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'		
            
      )		
)		
SELECT DISTINCT  		
		metal_atg.source_name, 
		metal_atg.load_type, 
		metal_atg.agency_nup, 
		metal_atg.created, 
		metal_atg.effective_date, 
		metal_atg.gw_producer_id, 
		metal_atg.id, 
		metal_atg.lob, 
		metal_atg.term_type, 
		metal_atg.term_reason_code, 
		metal_atg.modified,
		metal_atg.new_date,
		metal_atg.noticeto_agent,
		metal_atg.renewal_date,
		metal_atg.replaced_by,
		metal_atg.state,
		metal_atg.sub_code,
		metal_atg.type,
		current_batch.batch_id
FROM $$raw_schema.adm_termination_guidewire metal_atg		
CROSS JOIN current_batch		
ORDER BY 		
    metal_atg.id,		
    metal_atg.created,		
    metal_atg.modified;

fields.name: o_src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5(
	'source_name' || source_name || 
	'load_type' || load_type || 
	'o_agency_id' || to_char(o_agency_id) ||
	'type' || type ||
	'noticeto_agent' || noticeto_agent || 
	'o_new_business_termination_date' || to_char(o_new_business_termination_date)|| 
	'o_renewal_termination_date' || to_char(o_renewal_termination_date) ||
	'lob' || lob ||
	'term_type' || term_type ||
	'term_reason_code' || term_reason_code ||
	'replaced_by' || replaced_by ||
    'o_termination_guidewire_effective_date'|| to_char(o_termination_guidewire_effective_date)||
    'sub_code' || sub_code || 
    'gw_producer_id' || gw_producer_id || 
	'state' || state || 
	'o_termination_guidewire_datetime_created' || to_char(o_termination_guidewire_datetime_created) || 
	'o_termination_guidewire_datetime_modified' || to_char(o_termination_guidewire_datetime_modified)	
	)

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
      adm_termination_guidewire_row_id as termination_guidewire_row_id, 
      adm_termination_guidewire_row_md5checksum as termination_guidewire_row_md5checksum, 
      adm_termination_guidewire_batch_id as termination_guidewire_batch_id,  
	  agency_nup as agency_id,
      id as termination_guidewire_id,
      modified as termination_guidewire_datetime_modified,
      adm_termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime as termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime	
    FROM 
$$staging_schema.adm_termination_guidewire
    where  
adm_termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
